description:
It's hard to believe 10 years have passed since that fateful day. With the coincidental release of P.O.D.'s &quot;Satellite&quot; album on 9/11/01 a somewhat successful San Diego band rocketed to the top of the charts and inspired millions to truly feel &quot;Alive&quot;

This fanmade album commemorates that occasion and pays tribute to the fallen thru songs like &quot;America&quot; featuring guitar legend Santana and a special World Trade Center mix of &quot;Ghetto&quot;. I also included their new 2011 song...21 tracks in all


To quote one of those songs,&quot;I believe this world believes in love&quot;
